reviewText: I recently bought this hoping it was a European version the American unplugged shows on mtv, instead i got a bunch of English plant  bootlegged videos, of him doing live acoustic shows, which are not good quality, but worth it to any led zeppelin fan, the cds are very good for a live hearing of zeppeling songs as well!

I don't believe that this is an official release. There are videos of performances like this available for free all over the internet. This seller most likely downloaded this "rare" performance from a peer sharing website, burned it to DVD, and wants to sell it to you for $40. Ch-ching!!!
Even the previous review sounds like a sales pitch.
Before you buy this ask yourself, "Have I ever heard of this release before? Are Robert Plant or Jimmy Page getting paid a dime for this?
Is this a BOOTLEG RECORDING?
A wonderful collection of music from two of rocks best artists laying the worlds best rock bands songs.  Please god full fledged Zeppelin reunion!

I bought this set and "LIGHT MY FIRE" 2 CD + DVD set for my friend who is a huge Led Zep fan. We all sat down to watch it and I was as enthralled as he was. It's a great DVD's and CD's...music, settings, singing...it's got it all.
